Kim Kardashian goofs off with her son Saint and tries out a blue-eyed Instagram filter as she takes her mind off custody drama with Kanye West She's been engaged in an escalating conflict with her estranged ex Kanye West in recent days. But Kim Kardashian seemed to put the drama aside on Tuesday as she enjoyed some bonding time with her oldest son Saint, six. The 41-year-old Keeping Up With The Kardashians star and her son appeared to be having a blast as they played around with an eerie blue-eye filter on her phone....read Kim Kardashian goofs off with Saint amid custody drama with Kanye West
